Package: molebie-ai
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Maintainer: Jimmy <jimmy@molebieai.com>
Homepage: https://molebieai.com
Description: Self-hosted privacy-first AI assistant
 Molebie AI is a fully self-hosted AI assistant platform with
 local LLM inference, web search, RAG, and voice features.
 This package installs the molebie-ai CLI tool.
